latestPosts.caption:
Doing this daily and not knowing which day it is :) 
Playsuit @yogvalley

Life gets 10x more entertaining when you have a @thechiragkhatri_ in it.
If you know him, you know.
If you don’t — that’s exactly why I’m writing this. 
He puts up with a lot of my crap.
But let’s not forget — he gives me just as much.
He bullies me daily, so it’s only fair I return the favour.

Can I go a day without poking him for no reason? No.
Do I ever win the banter? No.
Have I stopped trying? Also no.

He’s a kid. A weird kid.
I genuinely think he’s reversing age (mentally).
But every year, I see him becoming a better human — and I learn so much from him every single day.

He is the kind of friend you dream of having in your life.
Because here’s the thing: he’s the kind of person who makes even the crappiest days better.
He has multiple personalities, so you basically get every kind of friend in one.

He’s a menace.
But he’s my favourite human menace. 
HBD 🙂 
JMD 🙏
